description:

In which Jaime and Brienne are seeing the same therapist, cross paths by chance, and end up finding comfort in each other.

-

Brand new, experimental, modern AU fanfic for my fellow Braime fans! More coming soon. In the meantime, feel free to read, share your opinion, provide constructive critisicm, or ask any question you want.

Cheers!
